author: NEW YORK DAILY NEWS
title: Mighty Quinn: October 13
text: Has MQ even won a playoff game yet? Yikes! “Hey, Mighty. I’ve been an avid follower for 10 years now, enjoy your column very much. A while ago you printed the health benefits of apple cider vinegar and I didn't keep the article. But I would like to know them again if you could print it one more time. Anyway, I've tried apple cider vinegar and it seems to help quite a bit. My joints do feel better and my IBS seems better, but I forgot all the other benefits ACV gives your body. Also, would you explain what sirignanos are, I never understood that. “PS : I only live a couple miles from your encounter over the summer on Saratoga Lake at Stewart's with a fan,wish I had been there! Daniel Simard.” Check out Mighty Quinn: April 14, 2015 on nydailynews.com “Hey, Mighty, thanks for your quick response to my request, that site was awesome. Take care and keep your articles interesting as usual. I'll be reading you! Daniel Simard.” Mighty missed with the Astros on Monday and likes the Cubs on Tuesday. The deficit is 988 sirignanos.
